Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:37.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏大混乱！面堂家赏花宴！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 赏花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这下雪天吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想些什么？混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要在哪赏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好我家有最近才完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己专用的温室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温室太窄没气氛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令我意外 阿忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是面堂家的温室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 有5千平方公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约1万5千坪的幅地中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有原生兰 黑郁金香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至片片草皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方至北端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南则至极南之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的花草采集之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对其中每一种花草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都由电脑完全管理之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说是非常棒之温室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中被命名日本春之房的一角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天所开之花遍地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然代代相传于我家正统的樱花树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也种植于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 现在可是在上课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果汁真的好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信是果汁的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好喝的东西是生来头一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 以你星球而言的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去拿一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意 我们就喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望利用此机会能互相了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才希望达成 跳啊 蒙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来祝贺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你这家伙在此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老师 怎么用这家伙这种口气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不招呼一声随意到人家家之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用“你这家伙”就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那眼神算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定想我是来敲诈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确是领薪生活者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但领薪人有领薪人的口味及食物生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能了解吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用陶炉烤秋刀鱼之味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浸萝卜所结合的淡淡的盐味\N当我尝到此为之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心将成为极乐城向天空飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全英所提及之表现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上大和大国所传承
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本古来之味觉所相互结合的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是领薪人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐啊 我感谢自己是领薪生活者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能了解吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了什么不懂前后的长篇大论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没叫你来 我不允许你到我家赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们办的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想你们一定装着赏花\N而喝酒 所以我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那酒桶是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我星球的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解的话 就快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在的话果汁就不好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那幅样 喝的东西是果汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酒的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再多啰嗦看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你劈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我没醉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说！我没醉啦 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉姆 那是加酒精的果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没放酒精啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看 大家都醉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边 右边…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我喝喝 确定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和酒不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品质是绝无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对以下系列的星球之客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真没法子不再喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对地球人是“剧”药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“剧”药？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明书上有写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是有像醉酒之现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这症状停止之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会开始演话“剧”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是到业平办事的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年龄约在十六、七岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 酒加一壶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是金爷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子真有精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来一壶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 随时都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金爷真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真守得紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一来就如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息店的卷发先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！又出现夜间斩人者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金爷 把这夜间斩人的人捉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但传说金爷是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个游荡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就觉得金爷非平凡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个游荡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可就这么上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上舞台 请换上服装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原世间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜间将河…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 心情好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有何贵干！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用特写灯照射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还装出一幅帅样看来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是现流行的夜间斩人者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你运气真差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 你不知道我是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下所知之伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗本温泉人 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening,Mr. Perm?\N(发生什么了 卷发先生)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转换衣饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.\N(再来一次)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening,Mr. Perm?\N(发生什么事了 卷发先生)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last night,Tsujigiri appeared once again.\N(昨晚又有一件夜间杀人事件)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,my god\N(我的天啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the hotoke?\N(佛在哪里？)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,it is a good question.\N(这真是好问题)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the hotoke.\N(这就是佛)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy. See you again. Bye bye.\N(我很忙 再见了)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,Mr. Perm. Wait,wait.\N(卷发先生 等等)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful kiriguchi.\N(这刀口真是利落)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Gold?\N(金先生？)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think the murderer is tsujigiri.\N(我认为犯人就是夜间杀人者)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真听的我可损失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个游荡人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很正经
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得他们太呆没法子加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游荡人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是那个PLAYBOY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又到底怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾 火灾了！…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜店的小七
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火 火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了…火灾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用吵我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是粗野之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对晃荡的我而言真无法消受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是个平凡角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道出名号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在问我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就记着是游荡人的金爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会追丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是纹身出名之远山金志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是什么宣传或打信名度？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边也来了个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带听说每晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现夜间斩人魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 前次的那位武士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可在个奇怪之地相见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个奇怪之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的男士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这里是哪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金爷不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才杀人魔出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人家伙刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 金爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人魔怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说刚才被旅行人男人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你见到脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有让你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能斩你就斩看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一身纹身是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背上的章鱼可清楚的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然他是远山金志郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼是家传高尚的家纹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想斩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想斩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想斩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是执法者就不能让他活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大爷 我只是个游荡人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在此时说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说些后悔之语
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹爹 粥好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常在麻烦你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹爹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好不讲的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就喝个热粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时哥哥在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要谈他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是丢弃这个家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了 服了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真失礼了（植木等的笑料）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说我只是个游荡人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你那首级砍下 把那当作刀的铁锈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 我们为何做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像被拉姆的果汁弄醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后演戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在羞得无法在街上走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能嫁人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 吃了梅子 还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己是蔬菜店的小七
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再演 再来啊…让我看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我们并非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,农药吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这是拉姆小姐带的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部洒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没什么害处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以让大家快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在将这怠惰的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向梦想实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下炸弹才行？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“剧”不是在舞台上才能演的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受限的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受限的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受限的观众之下共谋的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市就是舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是相遇的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人即演员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切皆是剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的友引町
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最欠缺的是游玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一介之高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剧中成为全知全能之神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一件很简单之事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白影 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御面骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个游荡人金爷 说了好多次了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你化成刀之铁锈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个游荡人 金爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的达令稍微的错失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引来了冬国之少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被风雪包围的友引町
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的记忆要被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着 达令 春天就在面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的春天 寂寞的妖精物语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:10.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:23.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:36.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:50.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:55.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:59.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:12.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:15.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:25.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:30.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.72,0:24:36.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:41.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.20,0:24:49.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.18,0:24:53.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.06,0:24:57.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:25:01.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:05.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.72,0:25:09.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.64,0:25:12.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:16.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.48,0:25:20.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:27.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:31.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

